### DO NOT DO
- Remove either bridge URL (both are needed)
- Consolidate both bridges into single endpoint (architecturally wrong)
- Use Node.js middleware-gateway as replacement (CSNOtk is terminology, ABDM handles ABDM)

### ALWAYS REMEMBER
1. CSNOtk = Terminology service (medical term coding)
2. ABDM Bridge = ABDM communication (patient data sharing)
3. They are NOT interchangeable
4. Multiple HMS instances can use one ABDM Bridge (centralized)
5. CSNOtk is stateless lookup API (can be called directly or via bridge)
